	<div style="text-align:right;">
		MARUITI, Vanessa Pires<sup>1</sup>; HERRERA, Ana Cristina<sup>2</sup>; PINTO, Guilherme de Moraes<sup>3</sup>; MALACHIAS, Vania Aparecida Terra<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
